law.text:
In addition to its other powers and duties, the Commission shall:
review the operation of units of State and local government that have responsibility for implementation of the Plan;
provide a clearinghouse for information on the Patuxent River and its watershed;
review and comment on plans and reports related to the Patuxent River and its watershed; and
serve as the tributary strategy team for the Patuxent Watershed, coordinating the Patuxent tributary strategy with the Plan.
